I'm going to enjoy this while it lasts! <br>
<br>
Oh and a question, do any of you have your children make out Christmas lists?  Do you have difficulty getting them to oblige?<br>
<br>
God bless,<br>
Von <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#DEB887><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub98.ezboard.com/bsparrowshearth.showUserPublicProfile?gid=t0mmyt>T0mmyT</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle><img src=http://smilies.narno.com/smilies/yaplukon/dead.gif></span><br>  Posts: 498<br> <font color=#B87333>(12/1/03 5:48 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub98.ezboard.com/fsparrowshearthfrm12.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=27.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Please Explain This to Me?</span><hr size=1> OK, this is a HUGE secret and I may be throw out of the dads group for sharing, but what we do is give each kid a ten to be quiet and not argue and be prepared for school.<br>
