Well the week is over with, hubby goes back to work tomorrow.  And although he didn't get the treatment I usually do, there were some rough edges through the week.  And he doesn't know quite how to handle them.  I think he got a little frustrated at times.  But mostly I think the kids and I both enjoyed having him home.  I did get some shopping done and other things taken care of around the house.  He finally had time to get a couch put up down stairs and a new lock on the back door that was needed.  I think I only said once that he needed to go back to work! <!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.pluigs.com/stuff/smiles/pound.gif"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><br>
